@startuml
title UART 到网络时序图
!include _theme.iuml

participant "Flight Controller" as FC
participant "UART Port" as UART
participant "mavlink_bridge" as Bridge
participant "network_app / sockets" as Net
actor "PC / GCS" as Client

FC -> UART : 发送串口数据
UART -> Bridge : UART 接收任务读取
Bridge -> Bridge : 更新统计与回调
Bridge -> Net : 广播或发送网络数据
Net -> Client : 客户端收到回传
@enduml
